{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1149100, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一些人反对“民主化”是反对资产阶级法权下的只有少数资产阶级享有的民主（参考“反对资产阶级自由化”）\n另一些人反对民主化是觉得封建社会或者奴隶社会比较好", "timestamp": 1614346387, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149106, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "民主不是目的只是手段", "timestamp": 1614346426, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149110, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 同问", "timestamp": 1614346453, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149112, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 但是与民主相反的专制手段是万万要不得的啊！", "timestamp": 1614346460, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149115, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 目的是什么呢", "timestamp": 1614346487, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149120, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "威权不好吗", "timestamp": 1614346533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149125, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "理想中的民主是不存在的，复古的原教旨民主要抽签才民主", "timestamp": 1614346607, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149127, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 典型的二极管思维", "timestamp": 1614346657, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149128, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 理想中的民主是不存在的，所以满清封建君主专制也不错", "timestamp": 1614346661, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149130, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 为什么好呢？除非自己被假设为受益者", "timestamp": 1614346664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 我理解的民主并不是非黑即白，而是可以分等级的。从最专制到最民主之间可以划分许多民主等级，不同社会情况适合不同民主等级，但是历史的大趋势是随着社会进步，民主等级会不断提升。", "timestamp": 1614346807, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149159, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你这就是论证滑坡了", "timestamp": 1614346950, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149172, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 确实，民主集中制也是一种符合中国国情的民主，未来的理想状态是共产主义民主", "timestamp": 1614347010, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149176, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 当你看到一个人拿着批判**部落制民主**的话术来批判**资产阶级代议制民主**的时候，比起直接认为他是**无产阶级民主**的支持者，最好还是警惕一下对面是不是个**封建专制**人", "timestamp": 1614347023, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149177, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: yysy,qs", "timestamp": 1614347051, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149182, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对对对，您说的都对", "timestamp": 1614347153, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149198, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我也觉得，现在有些人提倡的既不是社会主义也不是资本主义，而是封建主义。这种人多半还自认为是左派，丢左派的脸hh", "timestamp": 1614347258, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1149217, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 历史上资本主义国家“民主”的含义也是在不断扩大的，那么我们是不是也可以走资产阶级民主化的道路，最后渐变到真正的由全体民众享有的民主呢？", "timestamp": 1614347476, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1151820, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 您就是伯恩施坦？", "timestamp": 1614393714, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1152089, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 227251, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 畅想而已", "timestamp": 1614397022, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 227251, "reply": 20, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "#政治相关# 我真的想不通啊  渐进的民主化意味着随着国家的进步，国家制度会朝着民主方向变革。  如果否定民主化的价值，那就意味着这个社会的民主程度保持不变或者向着专制发展？？？？真的想不通，后者有什么可行性？", "timestamp": 1614346243, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1614397019, "url": "", "vote": {}}}